重复 我们遭遇攻击
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I repeat, we are under assault.

56
00:00:37,180 --> 00:00:40,770
引擎失灵 救生系统损坏
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The engines are dead, life support failing.

57
00:00:40,770 --> 00:00:44,060
请求附近战船营救
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Requesting aid from any vessel within range.

58
00:00:44,060 --> 00:00:48,070
我们距离阿斯加德22个跳跃点
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are 22 jump points out of Asgard.

59
00:00:48,070 --> 00:00:50,610
我们的船员均是阿斯加德的家庭成员
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our crew is made up of Asgardian families.

60
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:52,360
只有少数的战士
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We have very few soldiers here.

61
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:54,320
我们不是军用飞船
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is not a warcraft.

62
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:56,330
重复 我们不是军用飞船
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I repeat, this is not a warcraft.

63
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:12,720
仔细听我说
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hear me and rejoice.

64
00:01:16,550 --> 00:01:18,810
被伟大的泰坦神所拯救
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You have had the privilege

65
00:01:18,850 --> 00:01:21,560
是你们莫大的荣幸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of being saved by the Great Titan.

66
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:26,690
或许你们认为这是受难
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You may think this is suffering.

67
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,070
不
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.

68
00:01:30,110 --> 00:01:32,360
这是救赎
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is salvation.

69
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:40,120
正是因为你们的牺牲
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Universal scales tip toward balance

70
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,700
宇宙才趋于平衡
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because of your sacrifice.

71
00:01:43,410 --> 00:01:44,830
微笑吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Smile.

72
00:01:46,170 --> 00:01:48,290
因为即使告别尘世
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For even in death,

73
00:01:48,290 --> 00:01:50,670
你们也是灭霸的子民
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you have become Children of Thanos.

74
00:02:06,190 --> 00:02:08,230
我知道失败的滋味
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know what it's like to lose.

75
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:13,360
明知自己没有错 却还是失败了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To feel so desperately that you're right...

76
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:16,740
这种绝望的感觉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}yet to fail, nonetheless.

77
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:26,540
很可怕
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's frightening.

78
00:02:27,790 --> 00:02:29,750
让人不寒而栗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Turns the legs to jelly.

79
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,170
但我想问问你 结局会如何
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I ask you, to what end?

80
00:02:35,510 --> 00:02:38,180
畏惧还是逃避
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dread it, run from it...

81
00:02:39,220 --> 00:02:41,640
命运终会降临
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}destiny arrives all the same.

82
00:02:42,810 --> 00:02:44,680
而现在 它已在眼前
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And now, it's here.

83
00:02:45,350 --> 00:02:47,230
或者我应该说
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or should I say...

84
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,110
我已在你面前
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am.

85
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,740
你废话太多了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You talk too much.

86
00:02:57,950 --> 00:02:59,820
超能立方
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The Tesseract.

87
00:02:59,820 --> 00:03:02,120
还是你哥哥的人头
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or your brother's head.

88
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:09,170
我相信你已经选好了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I assume you have a preference.

89
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:11,670
噢 当然了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, I do.

90
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,130
想杀就杀吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Kill away.

91
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,440
够了 住手
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, stop!

92
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:37,240
我们没有超能立方
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We don't have the Tesseract.

93
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,860
它已经在阿斯加德被毁掉了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was destroyed on Asgard.

94
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:52,630
你真是史上最差劲的弟弟
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You really are the worst brother.

95
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,720
我向你保证 哥哥
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I assure you, brother...

96
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,800
太阳会再次照耀我们
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the sun will shine on us again.

97
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:06,930
你过于乐观了 阿斯加德人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your optimism is misplaced, Asgardian.

98
00:04:06,930 --> 00:04:11,020
我要声明一点 我不是阿斯加德人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, for one thing, I'm not Asgardian.

99
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:12,230
还有一点呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And for another...

100
00:04:14,610 --> 00:04:15,820
我们有浩克
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we have a Hulk.

101
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,830
让他玩
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let him have his fun.

102
00:05:22,050 --> 00:05:23,630
天父啊
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Allfathers...

103
00:05:25,550 --> 00:05:28,720
让黑魔法再一次流经我的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}let the dark magic flow through me one last...

104
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,680
身体吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}time.

105
00:05:45,530 --> 00:05:46,910
你这就不对了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That was a mistake.

106
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,580
不
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No!

107
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:06,390
你要为此偿命
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're going to die for that.

108
00:06:09,470 --> 00:06:10,640
嘘
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Shh.

109
00:06:17,610 --> 00:06:19,400
我谦虚的个体
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My humble personage...

110
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:22,940
在您的伟大前鞠躬
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}bows before your grandeur.

111
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:29,910
任何人都不曾享有
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No other being has ever had the might...

112
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:31,950
使用哪怕一颗无限原石的尊崇
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}nay, the nobility...

113
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:36,710
更不用说两颗了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to wield not one, but two Infinity Stones.

114
00:06:40,090 --> 00:06:44,630
宇宙臣服于您的掌下
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The universe lies within your grasp.

115
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:26,630
地球上还有两颗原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are two more stones on Earth.

116
00:07:28,010 --> 00:07:31,850
我的孩子们啊 去找到它们 给我带回泰坦星
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Find them, my children, and bring them to me on Titan.

117
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:33,510
父亲 我们不会让您失望的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Father, we will not fail you.

118
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:36,020
请容我打断一下
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I might interject.

119
