01:04:19,210 --> 01:04:22,130
所以我说 我们将战火引到他那儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I say we take the fight to him.

1028
01:04:22,130 --> 01:04:23,130
博士
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Doctor.

1029
01:04:24,930 --> 01:04:26,470
你同意吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you concur?

1030
01:04:29,010 --> 01:04:31,470
好吧 史塔克 我们去找他
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, Stark. We go to him.

1031
01:04:32,560 --> 01:04:34,940
但你必须要明白
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you have to understand...

1032
01:04:34,940 --> 01:04:36,520
如果我需要在救你 还有那个孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if it comes to saving you

1033
01:04:36,520 --> 01:04:39,230
和时间原石中做选择的话
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or the kid or the Time Stone...

1034
01:04:39,230 --> 01:04:42,990
我会毫不犹豫地放弃你们俩的生命
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will not hesitate to let either of you die.

1035
01:04:42,990 --> 01:04:47,160
我不能失去原石 整个宇宙的希望都在它身上
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't, because the universe depends on it.

1036
01:04:47,160 --> 01:04:50,080
很好 提前说清楚道德标准
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nice. Good, moral compass.

1037
01:04:51,330 --> 01:04:52,910
那就这样说定了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're straight.

1038
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:55,410
好了 孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, kid.

1039
01:04:56,670 --> 01:04:57,880
你正式是复仇者的一员了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're an Avenger now.

1040
01:05:34,370 --> 01:05:36,580
我觉得你可能饿了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you might be hungry.

1041
01:05:48,720 --> 01:05:50,510
我一直恨那把椅子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I always hated that chair.

1042
01:05:50,510 --> 01:05:53,260
我听说了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I've been told.

1043
01:05:53,260 --> 01:05:57,230
即便这样 我也希望你有一天能坐上它
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Even so, I'd hoped you'd sit in it one day.

1044
01:05:58,020 --> 01:05:59,440
我恨这个房间
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hated this room.

1045
01:06:00,350 --> 01:06:01,730
这架飞船
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This ship.

1046
01:06:01,730 --> 01:06:03,570
我恨我的人生
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hated my life.

1047
01:06:08,070 --> 01:06:10,280
你也跟我说过了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You told me that too.

1048
01:06:13,410 --> 01:06:14,910
每一天
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Every day.

1049
01:06:17,580 --> 01:06:19,540
我听了近二十年
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For almost 20 years.

1050
01:06:22,170 --> 01:06:24,500
你带走我时 我还只是个孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was a child when you took me.

1051
01:06:25,420 --> 01:06:26,670
我救了你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I saved you.

1052
01:06:30,260 --> 01:06:31,090
不
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.

1053
01:06:32,680 --> 01:06:36,430
不是 我们曾经快乐地生活在我的母星上
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. We were happy on my home planet.

1054
01:06:36,430 --> 01:06:38,180
每天在饥饿中入睡
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Going to bed hungry...

1055
01:06:38,180 --> 01:06:40,100
以拾荒为生
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}scrounging for scraps.

1056
01:06:40,100 --> 01:06:43,060
你的星球已经在崩溃的边缘了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your planet was on the brink of collapse.

1057
01:06:43,060 --> 01:06:45,480
是我拯救了那一切
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm the one who stopped that.

1058
01:06:45,480 --> 01:06:47,490
你知道后来发生了什么吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you know what's happened since then?

1059
01:06:47,490 --> 01:06:49,700
新生儿们
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The children born...

1060
01:06:49,700 --> 01:06:53,320
在蓝天下过着富足的生活
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}have known nothing but full bellies and clear skies.

1061
01:06:53,320 --> 01:06:54,530
那里成了天堂
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a paradise.

1062
01:06:57,290 --> 01:06:59,290
因为你杀掉了星球上一半的人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because you murdered half the planet.

1063
01:06:59,290 --> 01:07:02,330
那只是为了救赎而付出的小小代价而已
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A small price to pay for salvation.

1064
01:07:02,330 --> 01:07:03,460
你疯了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're insane.

1065
01:07:03,460 --> 01:07:05,590
小家伙 这是一道简单的算术题
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Little one, it's a simple calculus.

1066
01:07:05,590 --> 01:07:09,050
宇宙是有限的 它的资源也是有限的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This universe is finite, its resources finite.

1067
01:07:09,050 --> 01:07:13,390
如果对生命不加以约束 它最终将走向消亡
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If life is left unchecked, life will cease to exist.

1068
01:07:13,390 --> 01:07:14,600
它需要矫正
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It needs correction.

1069
01:07:14,600 --> 01:07:16,100
你不能妄下定论
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't know that!

1070
01:07:17,520 --> 01:07:20,390
我是唯一一个看清的人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm the only one who knows that.

1071
01:07:20,390 --> 01:07:24,560
至少我是唯一愿意付出行动的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At least, I'm the only one with the will to act on it.

1072
01:07:26,230 --> 01:07:27,230
曾经
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For a time...

1073
01:07:29,690 --> 01:07:34,120
与我并肩战斗的你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you had that same will...

1074
01:07:35,570 --> 01:07:38,120
也有着共同的信仰
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as you fought by my side.

1075
01:07:38,830 --> 01:07:40,040
女儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Daughter.

1076
01:07:40,660 --> 01:07:42,500
我不是你的女儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not your daughter.

1077
01:07:45,040 --> 01:07:47,670
我痛恨你教给我的一切东西
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything I hate about myself you taught me.

1078
01:07:48,500 --> 01:07:50,090
正是这些
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And, in doing so,

1079
01:07:50,090 --> 01:07:52,300
让你成为银河中最勇敢无畏的女人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}made you the fiercest woman in the galaxy.

1080
01:07:55,220 --> 01:07:58,100
所以我当时才派你去寻找灵魂原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why I trusted you to find the Soul Stone.

1081
01:08:01,390 --> 01:08:04,270
抱歉我让你失望了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry I disappointed you.

1082
01:08:05,400 --> 01:08:08,070
我的确很失望
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am disappointed.

1083
01:08:08,070 --> 01:08:10,440
但不是因为你没有找到
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But not because you didn't find it.

1084
01:08:14,200 --> 01:08:15,700
而是因为你找到了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But because you did.

1085
01:08:17,280 --> 01:08:19,080
却对我说谎了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you lied.

1086
01:08:36,180 --> 01:08:37,260
星云
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nebula.

1087
01:08:44,480 --> 01:08:45,850
不要这样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't do this.

1088
01:08:45,900 --> 01:08:47,310
不久以前
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Some time ago,

1089
01:08:47,310 --> 01:08:50,190
你妹妹潜入这架飞船来刺杀我
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your sister snuck aboard this ship to kill me.

1090
01:08:50,230 --> 01:08:51,280
求求你 别这样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please don't do this.

1091
01:08:51,280 --> 01:08:53,530
她差点就成功了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And very nearly succeeded.

1092
01:08:54,240 --> 01:08:55,610
所以我把她带到这里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I brought her here.

1093
01:08:57,240 --> 01:08:58,450
来谈一谈
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To talk.

1094
01:09:06,170 --> 01:09:08,500
停下 住手
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop. Stop it.

1095
01:09:14,420 --> 01:09:17,260
我以我的性命起誓
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I swear to you on my life.

1096
01:09:17,260 --> 01:09:19,510
我没有找到灵魂原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I never found the Soul Stone.

1097
01:09:23,600 --> 01:09:25,390
读取记忆档案
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Accessing memory files.

1098
01:09:25,430 --> 01:09:26,810
你知道他打算做什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what he's about to do.

1099
01:09:26,810 --> 01:09:29,610
现在他终于准备好了 他要去掠夺原石了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's finally ready, and he's going for the stones.

1100
01:09:29,610 --> 01:09:30,820
-全部原石 -他不可能得到全部的原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- All of them. - He can never get them all.

1101
01:09:30,820 --> 01:09:31,900
他会的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He will!

1102
01:09:31,900 --> 01:09:34,190
他不会的 星云
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He can't, Nebula.

1103
01:09:34,190 --> 01:09:36,610
因为我找到了通往灵魂原石的地图
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because I found the map to the Soul Stone...

1104
01:09:36,610 --> 01:09:39,450
然后我把它烧成了灰 我烧掉了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I burned it to ash. I burned it.

1105
01:09:44,450 --> 01:09:46,290
你的坚强
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're strong.

1106
01:09:48,330 --> 01:09:49,330
是我教的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Me.

1107
01:09:51,790 --> 01:09:53,460
你的慷慨
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're generous.

1108
01:09:54,760 --> 01:09:55,760
也是我教的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Me.

1109
01:09:57,760 --> 01:10:00,430
但我从未教过你说谎
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But I never taught you to lie.

1110
01:10:00,430 --> 01:10:03,140
难怪你撒谎如此拙劣
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why you're so bad at it.

1111
01:10:05,310 --> 01:10:09,730
灵魂原石在哪里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is the Soul Stone?

1112
01:10:27,250 --> 01:10:28,250
沃米尔星
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Vormir!

1113
01:10:46,350 --> 01:10:47,850
灵魂原石在沃米尔星
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The stone is on Vormir.

1114
01:10:51,270 --> 01:10:53,650
带路
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Show me.

1115
01:10:55,520 --> 01:10:56,900
我是格鲁特
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am Groot.

1116
01:10:56,900 --> 01:10:58,280
尿在杯子里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tinkle in the cup.

1117
01:10:58,280 --> 01:10:59,700
我们不看 有什么好看的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're not looking. What's there to see?

1118
01:10:59,700 --> 01:11:01,950
害羞什么 谁没见过小树枝
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's a twig? Everybody's seen a twig before.

1119
01:11:01,950 --> 01:11:03,320
我是格鲁特
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am Groot.

1120
01:11:03,370 --> 01:11:04,450
小树 把杯子里的东西倒进太空
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tree, pour what's in the cup

1121
01:11:04,450 --> 01:11:06,290
再继续尿在里面
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}out into space and go in the cup again.

1122
01:11:06,290 --> 01:11:07,370
你会说格鲁特语
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You speak Groot?

1123
01:11:07,370 --> 01:11:09,540
嗯 我在阿斯加德选修过
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, they taught it on Asgard. It was an elective.

1124
01:11:09,540 --> 01:11:10,710
我是格鲁特
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am Groot.

1125
01:11:10,710 --> 01:11:12,830
我们快到的时候你就知道了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You'll know when we're close.

1126
01:11:12,880 --> 01:11:14,590
尼德威阿尔的熔炉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nidavellir's forge harnesses

1127
01:11:14,590 --> 01:11:16,750
能收集中子星喷发的能量
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}the blazing power of a neutron star.

1128
01:11:19,630 --> 01:11:21,630
我的锤子就是在那里铸造的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's the birthplace of my hammer.

1129
01:11:22,380 --> 01:11:24,220
它的力量十分惊人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's truly awesome.

1130
01:11:30,060 --> 01:11:33,350
好吧 是时候尽船长的职责了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay, time to be the captain.

1131
01:11:38,360 --> 01:11:40,530
你弟弟死了 是吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, dead brother, huh?

1132
01:11:40,530 --> 01:11:42,780
那确实挺伤感的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, that could be annoying.

1133
01:11:42,780 --> 01:11:44,700
嗯 他以前也死过
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, he's been dead before.

1134
01:11:46,080 --> 01:11:49,040
但是我觉得这次可能是真的了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But, no, this time I think it really might be true.

1135
01:11:49,080 --> 01:11:51,660
你还提到过你姐姐和爸爸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you said your sister and your dad?

1136
01:11:51,660 --> 01:11:53,580
都死了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Both dead.

1137
01:11:53,580 --> 01:11:55,710
那至少还有个妈妈是吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But still got a mom, though?

1138
01:11:55,750 --> 01:11:57,040
被一个黑暗精灵杀了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Killed by a dark elf.

1139
01:11:57,090 --> 01:11:58,380
最好的朋友呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A best friend?

1140
01:11:58,380 --> 01:11:59,630
心脏被刺穿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stabbed through the heart.

1141
01:12:02,930 --> 01:12:06,260
你确定你要参加这次特别的刺杀行动吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You sure you're up to this particular murder mission?

1142
01:12:08,470 --> 01:12:09,970
当然
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Absolutely.

1143
01:12:09,970 --> 01:12:13,730
怒火 复仇 愤怒 失落 悔恨
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rage and vengeance, anger, loss, regret...

1144
01:12:13,730 --> 01:12:15,440
都是我的动力
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}they're all tremendous motivators.

1145
01:12:15,440 --> 01:12:16,560
它们能让我保持头脑清醒
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They really clear the mind.

1146
01:12:16,610 --> 01:12:18,820
所以我准备好了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I'm good to go.

1147
01:12:18,820 --> 01:12:21,530
没错 但我们说的可是灭霸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, but this Thanos we're talkin' about...

1148
01:12:21,530 --> 01:12:23,900
他是最难对付的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}he's the toughest there is.

1149
01:12:23,900 --> 01:12:26,070
-那是他没有跟我打过 -他有
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Well, he's never fought me. - Yeah, he has.

1150
01:12:26,070 --> 01:12:28,410
他没有跟我打过两次
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's never fought me twice.

1151
01:12:28,410 --> 01:12:30,330
还有别忘了 我要拿到新锤子了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I'm getting a new hammer, don't forget.

1152
01:12:30,330 --> 01:12:32,540
那锤子最好厉害一点
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It better be some hammer.

1153
01:12:36,630 --> 01:12:39,670
我已经1500岁了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, I'm 1,500 years old.

1154
01:12:39,670 --> 01:12:41,840
我杀过两倍于这个数字的敌人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've killed twice as many enemies as that.

1155
01:12:41,840 --> 01:12:43,880
他们每一个都想置我于死地
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And every one of them would've rather killed me,

1156
01:12:43,880 --> 01:12:45,590
却没一个成功
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but none succeeded.

1157
01:12:45,630 --> 01:12:48,680
是命运要我活着
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm only alive because fate wants me alive.

1158
01:12:48,680 --> 01:12:51,640
灭霸只是这些混蛋中的一个
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanos is just the latest in a long line of bastards...

1159
01:12:51,640 --> 01:12:53,680
他也将尝到我复仇的怒火
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and he'll be the latest to feel my vengeance.

1160
01:12:53,680 --> 01:12:55,600
这也是命运的安排
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fate wills it so.

1161
01:12:55,600 --> 01:12:56,940


1162
01:12:56,940 --> 01:12:58,810
那万一你错了呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And what if you're wrong?

1163
01:13:02,030 --> 01:13:03,860
如果我错了 那
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I'm wrong, then...

1164
01:13:05,110 --> 01:13:06,740
我还有什么可失去的呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}what more could I lose?

1165
01:13:20,590 --> 01:13:21,960
我能失去的还有很多
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I could lose a lot.

1166
01:13:21,960 --> 01:13:24,050
我在世上还有很多牵挂
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Me, personally, I could lose a lot.

1167
01:13:27,890 --> 01:13:28,890
好吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay.

1168
01:13:31,970 --> 01:13:34,140
如果命运真的想让你杀死那个王八蛋
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If fate does want you to kill that crapsack...

1169
01:13:34,140 --> 01:13:36,060
你就不能只有一只眼睛
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you're gonna need more than one stupid eyeball.

1170
01:13:36,060 --> 01:13:38,520
-这是什么 -这看起来像什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What's this? - What's it look like?

1171
01:13:38,520 --> 01:13:41,150
一个混球在康特阿克夏星打赌输给了我
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Some jerk lost a bet with me on Contraxia.

1172
01:13:41,150 --> 01:13:42,530
他把眼睛给你了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He gave you his eye?

1173
01:13:42,530 --> 01:13:43,780
才不是 他给了我100个筹码
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, he gave me 100 credits.

1174
01:13:43,780 --> 01:13:46,740
我当晚溜进他的房间偷走了他的眼睛
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I snuck into his room later that night and stole his eye.

1175
01:13:48,660 --> 01:13:49,950
谢谢 可爱的兔兔
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank you, sweet rabbit.

1176
01:13:49,950 --> 01:13:50,950


1177
01:13:53,580 --> 01:13:55,000
嗯
