1486
01:38:21,130 --> 01:38:24,510
灭霸只会得到灰烬和鲜血
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanos will have nothing but dust and blood.

1487
01:38:27,930 --> 01:38:29,890
我们的血多得是
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We have blood to spare.

1488
01:38:41,150 --> 01:38:42,610
他们投降了吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They surrender?

1489
01:38:43,440 --> 01:38:44,490
没有
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not exactly.

1490
01:39:11,470 --> 01:39:12,970
