1508
01:41:06,040 --> 01:41:07,590
瓦坎达万岁
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wakanda forever!

1509
01:41:20,060 --> 01:41:21,060
就现在
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now!

1510
01:41:51,300 --> 01:41:52,800
还要多久 苏睿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How much longer, Shuri?

1511
01:41:52,800 --> 01:41:54,550
我才刚刚开始 哥哥
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've barely begun, brother.

1512
01:41:54,550 --> 01:41:56,430
你最好加快速度
