{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Allfathers, give me strength.

1514
01:42:05,480 --> 01:42:07,480
你明白吗 孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You understand, boy?

1515
01:42:07,480 --> 01:42:10,480
你将会承受一颗星球的全部力量
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're about to take the full force of a star.

1516
01:42:11,440 --> 01:42:13,490
你会死的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It'll kill you.

1517
01:42:13,490 --> 01:42:15,650
真死了再说
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Only if I die.

1518
01:42:16,110 --> 01:42:17,490
没错
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.

1519
01:42:17,490 --> 01:42:20,330
这就是“死”的意思
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's what killing you means.

1520
01:42:48,310 --> 01:42:50,230
坚持 坚持住 索尔
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hold it! Hold it, Thor!

1521
01:43:40,610 --> 01:43:42,580
索尔 说句话 拜托
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thor! Say something. Come on.

1522
01:43:43,530 --> 01:43:44,540
索尔 你还好吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thor, you okay?

1523
01:43:50,250 --> 01:43:51,630
