{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He needs the axe!

1525
01:43:54,960 --> 01:43:56,420
斧柄在哪里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where's the handle?

1526
01:43:59,470 --> 01:44:01,760
树人 快帮我找找斧柄
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tree, help me find the handle!

1527
01:45:10,660 --> 01:45:12,830
它们的数量太多了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's too many of 'em!

1528
01:45:39,400 --> 01:45:42,740
