{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You guys are so screwed now!

1529
01:45:45,990 --> 01:45:48,030
给我把灭霸叫来
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bring me Thanos!

1530
01:46:20,780 --> 01:46:22,360
啊 没错
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, yeah.

1531
01:46:25,490 --> 01:46:27,490
灭霸人如其名
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're much more of a Thanos.

1532
01:46:29,740 --> 01:46:31,910
看来乌木喉已经死了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I take it the Maw is dead.

1533
01:46:34,120 --> 01:46:36,710
