{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still, he accomplished his mission.

1535
01:46:40,960 --> 01:46:42,590
你会后悔的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You may regret that.

1536
01:46:43,420 --> 01:46:44,800
他让你和至尊法师
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He brought you face-to-face

1537
01:46:44,800 --> 01:46:46,340
正面对决
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}with the Master of the Mystic Arts.

1538
01:46:49,470 --> 01:46:51,850
你认为他把你带到了哪儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And where do you think he brought you?

1539
01:46:52,930 --> 01:46:55,680
让我猜猜 你的家乡吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me guess. Your home?

1540
01:46:59,980 --> 01:47:01,400
曾经是
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It was.

1541
01:47:04,030 --> 01:47:05,570
过去它是那么的美
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And it was beautiful.

1542
01:47:08,070 --> 01:47:10,740
泰坦像许多其他的星球那样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Titan was like most planets.

1543
01:47:10,780 --> 01:47:13,790
人口太多 资源却不够
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Too many mouths, not enough to go around.

