1545
01:47:18,000 --> 01:47:19,920
大屠杀
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Genocide.

1546
01:47:19,960 --> 01:47:24,000
随机 公正 无论贫富贵贱
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But random, dispassionate, fair to rich and poor alike.

1547
01:47:25,460 --> 01:47:28,180
