{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And what I predicted came to pass.

1549
01:47:33,140 --> 01:47:35,350
那恭喜你了 你可真是个预言家
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Congratulations, you're a prophet.

1550
01:47:35,810 --> 01:47:37,100
我是个幸存者
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm a survivor.

1551
01:47:37,140 --> 01:47:39,600
一个想杀死亿万人的幸存者
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who wants to murder trillions.

1552
01:47:39,650 --> 01:47:43,820
集齐六块原石 我只需要轻松地打个响指
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With all six stones, I could simply snap my fingers.

1553
01:47:43,820 --> 01:47:48,610
他们就不复存在了 这是我的仁慈
