1558
01:48:04,500 --> 01:48:09,090
你马上就会知道我们的意志也跟你的一样强
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think you'll find our will equal to yours.

1559
01:48:10,630 --> 01:48:11,640
我们的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Our?

1560
01:48:17,680 --> 01:48:19,140
小菜一碟 奎尔
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Piece of cake, Quill.

