1589
01:51:27,670 --> 01:51:28,750
卡魔拉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gamora.

1590
01:51:32,670 --> 01:51:34,000
什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?

1591
01:51:34,000 --> 01:51:36,090
他带她去了沃米尔星
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He took her to Vormir.

1592
01:51:36,090 --> 01:51:38,050
