1617
01:54:21,170 --> 01:54:23,340
撤退 撤退 快
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fall back! Fall back, now!

1618
01:54:32,850 --> 01:54:35,100
山姆 瞄准左翼开火
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Focus that fire on the left flank, Sam.

1619
01:54:35,100 --> 01:54:36,190
